metadata.name: New Edit 1/1
metadata.description:
Within the postindustrial, a rediscovery of otherness and elsewheres. Concerned global citizens for urban survival. Personal narratives oscillate on the periphery of status and official outsider capacity. Styled button up, straight line cut, rain slicker trench coats, softly faded pencil skirts, dark printed tights. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of three beautiful tanned female model best friends with blue hair, wearing intricate versace styled oversized streetwear blue and green coats with buttons and casual dark gray sweatpants, walking near the brooklyn bridge in the 2000s in early autumn at midnight, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 85, scale: 11.
